# Install spacy and its 3 english models(small, medium, large) in Anaconda:

Step 1: Open Anaconda command prompt and activate the environment in which you want install the spacy

	To activate the required environment:

		conda activate environment_name



Step 2: To install spacy with specific version
		
		conda install -c conda-forge spacy=2.0.18


		To install spacy with latest version

		conda install -c conda-forge spacy


Step 3: To install english models version = 2.0.0

		pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_sm-2.0.0/en_core_web_sm-2.0.0.tar.gz
		pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_md-2.0.0/en_core_web_md-2.0.0.tar.gz
		pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_lg-2.0.0/en_core_web_lg-2.0.0.tar.gz

		To install english models with latest version

		python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm
		python -m spacy download en_core_web_md
		python -m spacy download en_core_web_lg